king upgrades
  - trigger for buying upgrades
  - map research to king property based on trigger player
  - update king property on table
  - update kings stats
  - give king spells/abilities when conditions are met

king control
  - kings start belonging to players 17 and 18
  - kings can be controlled by players 1-16
  - when a player clicks king, transfer control to that player
  - when a player with higher elo clicks king, transfer control to that player
  - 3 players can vote to transfer control to a new player

